  "text": "Recent work points to the existence of lineage-specific progenitors [CITATION_1] . One hypothesis for the switch from DL to UL neuron production mediated by Ntf3 would be the preferential effect of Ntf3 on UL specific progenitors (Franco and Muller, 2013) , promoting their premature differentiation.",
